gamers which a lot of people

00:05:31.530 --> 00:05:35.070
think are the gamers of
US or Europe or wherever.

00:05:35.070 --> 00:05:36.900
We are not a gaming
nation, and we

00:05:36.900 --> 00:05:40.780
are having our first brush
of gaming with smartphones.

00:05:40.780 --> 00:05:43.060
And hence, if any
of you are looking

00:05:43.060 --> 00:05:46.710
at building games
for India, don't

00:05:46.710 --> 00:05:48.700
get influenced by
your own likings,

00:05:48.700 --> 00:05:51.480
by your own things in which
you think that, hey, listen,

00:05:51.480 --> 00:05:53.380
I was playing this
