00:05:53.380 --> 00:05:57.050
or I love "Clash of Clans,"
and hence I need to do that.

00:05:57.050 --> 00:05:59.690
Think of that guy who
has no idea of gaming,

00:05:59.690 --> 00:06:01.670
it's his first
brush with gaming.

00:06:01.670 --> 00:06:02.550
Keep it simple.

00:06:02.550 --> 00:06:03.220
Keep it easy.

00:06:03.220 --> 00:06:05.510
Keep it casual.

00:06:05.510 --> 00:06:10.230
The things like text-based,
narrative-based, FTUE-based--

00:06:10.230 --> 00:06:12.060
first time user
experience-based--

00:06:12.060 --> 00:06:12.860
doesn't work.

00:06:12.860 --> 00:06:16.270
It's an easy pick up and
play game mechanics which--

00:06:16.270 --> 00:06:17.950
just keep it simple.

00:06:17.950 --> 00:06:19.810
You may sometimes
feel that hey listen,

00:06:19.810 --> 00:06:21.570
my game is really dumbed now.

00:06:21.570 --> 00:06:23.240
