KB and saying that boss,

00:06:47.200 --> 00:06:50.080
that needs to be optimized
and optimized and optimized

00:06:50.080 --> 00:06:50.870
relentlessly.

00:06:50.870 --> 00:06:53.453
I think these are the two things
which I kind of put in there.

00:06:53.453 --> 00:06:54.396
KUNAL SONI: OK, great.

