00:07:07.151 --> 00:07:09.750
VARUN KHURANA: So in our
case, the biggest thing

00:07:09.750 --> 00:07:13.840
that we have seen, and which
we kind of expected and was

00:07:13.840 --> 00:07:15.800
validated as a part
of the process,

00:07:15.800 --> 00:07:20.240
was just the repeated
behavior of consumers.

00:07:20.240 --> 00:07:25.370
